author: sussman
msg: Fix #1575:  ensure we never try to generate a diff on a binary-marked file.
* libsvn_client/diff.c (diff_file_changed):  if either file has a
binary mime-type, don't attempt to generate a diff at all.  Just
output a warning and exit early.

Remove a "###" comment about whether "--revprop" should be "--rev-prop".
